Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.91,0:02:05.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在距离和长谷市市政府西南5公里处
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.83,0:02:07.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,观测到大规模的威兹曼偏差
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.46,0:02:12.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是赤王迦具都玄示的达摩克利斯之剑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.54,0:02:15.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙要来真的了  羽张
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.13,0:02:17.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  事情开始变得有趣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.05,0:02:19.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是开玩笑的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.76,0:02:22.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们双方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.30,0:02:26.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赤之氏族炼狱舍与青之氏族Scepter4在决出雌雄之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.81,0:02:31.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又或者在一方死绝之前都要不计余力地战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.19,0:02:34.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世上没有比这更愉快的事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.07,0:02:37.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别说这么恐怖的话  善条
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.19,0:02:41.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们Scepter4是肩负国家安定的氏族
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.16,0:02:44.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在立场上并不能参与这种不要命的战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.24,0:02:49.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是真和他们同归于尽  那就等于我们输了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.91,0:02:53.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,盐津  你这大道理就留着去和羽张争论吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.54,0:02:56.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只负责斩杀眼前的敌人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.42,0:02:59.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是对牛弹琴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.97,0:03:01.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说了  这不是开玩笑的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.39,0:03:03.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,盐津
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.84,0:03:08.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管我们的看法如何  他们可没打算罢手啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.11,0:03:23.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,盐津
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.00,0:03:32.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有人都下车  快跳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.56,0:03:54.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这算是迦具都玄示的见面礼吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.98,0:03:59.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是疯了  居然还把无辜的市民卷入
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.32,0:04:02.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做出这种事真的还能原谅吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.49,0:04:05.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迦具都不需要得到任何人的谅解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.95,0:04:08.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,王就是这样的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.17,0:04:20.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也是斩杀该杀之人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.34,0:04:22.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不需要任何理由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.02,0:04:32.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,炼狱舍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.53,0:04:42.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太慢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.40,0:04:45.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然是用刀背砍的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.61,0:04:47.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但死了可别怪我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.99,0:04:52.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,善条…  别脑子一热就冲出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.34,0:05:09.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,远在数公里之外还能发动攻击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.85,0:05:12.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迦具都玄示真是太可怕了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.39,0:05:16.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你别冲在第一线啊  羽张
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.52,0:05:18.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为你挡子弹是我的工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.48,0:05:22.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有其他很多事等着你去做呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.98,0:05:25.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说什么傻话  除了保护你我还能做什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.45,0:05:29.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Scepter4 拔刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.59,0:05:45.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前进
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.64,0:05:53.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光之刃在混沌之中开辟道路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.43,0:05:58.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是秩序的力量  青王的意志
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.06,0:05:59.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.06,0:06:04.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,王之间的力量相互冲撞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.78,0:06:07.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带来更深的混沌之时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.32,0:06:13.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这把刀刃究竟又能斩断什么呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.25,0:06:21.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不许后退
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.42,0:06:22.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不许后退
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.72,0:06:28.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.22,0:06:33.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,挥刀太随意了  把它当做真刀打下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.97,0:06:34.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,楠原
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.22,0:06:35.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.86,0:06:51.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再…再来一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.07,0:06:54.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等你喘口气再说吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.74,0:06:58.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来日高还挺喜欢楠原的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.62,0:07:01.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  我也挺喜欢他的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.75,0:07:04.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每次的假动作都能骗到他  还挺好玩的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.26,0:07:10.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,善条先生  您觉得如何
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.34,0:07:15.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家看上去都非常有气势  我觉得不错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.76,0:07:22.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我听宗像室长说  善条先生是前任青王的亲信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.65,0:07:27.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还说您的剑技至今无人能及
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.28,0:07:30.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  这都是过去的事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.78,0:07:34.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您太谦虚了  请指导两招吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.16,0:07:36.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  这就算了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.74,0:07:40.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剑术指导顾问看上去很为难啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.66,0:07:42.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世理做事也太过认真了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.87,0:07:45.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他再强也已经是个退休很久的大叔吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.92,0:07:51.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  善条先生他真的很强啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.76,0:07:54.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么楠原  你们认识？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.64,0:07:59.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上星期  我半夜跑到中庭去自主训练
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.18,0:08:02.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁在那里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.31,0:08:08.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是  我是击剑机动科第四小队的楠原刚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.57,0:08:11.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  吓到了你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.82,0:08:15.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是庶务科资料室的善条刚毅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.24,0:08:17.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉打扰你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.08,0:08:28.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那把木刀看上去好大啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.38,0:08:31.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,单手挥得动那把刀吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.11,0:08:53.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀  真是无懈可击的拔刀术
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.03,0:08:58.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是鬼之善条  真是毫无死角
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.28,0:09:01.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他居然对着室长杀了过去？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.12,0:09:04.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不是说杀了过去  就是空挥了一剑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.21,0:09:07.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之那气势真的很骇人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.51,0:09:18.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我失陪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.80,0:09:20.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.60,0:09:22.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,室长？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.35,0:09:27.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  我看来是被他讨厌了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.23,0:09:29.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,楠原
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.52,0:09:32.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,离开道场记得锁门
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.86,0:09:38.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后第二天  我去庶务科资料室还钥匙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.95,0:09:41.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就看到了因电脑故障而一脸为难的善条先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.50,0:09:51.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后我就叫来了榎本  帮他修好了电脑  他很感谢我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.46,0:09:54.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚饭为我们煮了荞麦面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.05,0:09:57.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么鬼  怎么还有这段小插曲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.97,0:09:59.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那天的荞麦面真好吃  阿榎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.30,0:10:02.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那天日高也在啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.35,0:10:04.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您意下如何
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.85,0:10:09.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,淡岛副长  恳请指教
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.36,0:10:12.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他这是上去解围？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.27,0:10:13.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,胆量还挺大的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.15,0:10:16.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也可以说不知天高地厚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.53,0:10:17.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.15,0:10:18.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.25,0:10:32.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,楠原  还站得起来吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.59,0:10:34.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来是不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.84,0:10:36.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那边的  把他扶到角落去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.30,0:10:37.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.55,0:10:41.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么干脆就败下阵来的人  这里还真找不出第二个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.05,0:10:45.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋你别乱说  我可看好你啊  楠原
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.89,0:10:49.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.02,0:10:50.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紧急出动信号
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.81,0:10:54.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全员换上正式装备后在停车场集合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.78,0:10:58.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,副长  楠原他怎么办
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.44,0:11:00.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原地静养
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.41,0:11:04.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这样  今天你就在这偷懒吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.83,0:11:06.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.41,0:11:14.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天的行动  虽然只是解决多名异能者之间的打架
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.92,0:11:16.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我们的包围网也差点被他们突破
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.75,0:11:19.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为那群小贼之中还有几个实力强劲的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.67,0:11:21.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当时真的太险了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.80,0:11:22.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你被逮捕了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.64,0:11:26.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阝级异能者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.26,0:11:31.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果加入了氏族  那可就是干部级的实力啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.73,0:11:37.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要制服这样的人  这边的实力如果达不到队长级也挺累的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.07,0:11:40.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才要组织重新整编吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.86,0:11:45.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  为了应对阝级异能者而设置的精锐部队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.37,0:11:49.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全员都是队长级的梦幻部队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.12,0:11:51.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想想就热血沸腾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.71,0:11:53.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这还真不错呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.67,0:11:56.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你干嘛一副事不关己的口气啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.25,0:11:59.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也要挤进那支精锐部队啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.09,0:12:02.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以从今天开始特训  特训啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.01,0:12:02.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.06,0:12:10.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该去特训啦…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.44,0:12:14.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,室长又来了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.85,0:12:18.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您觉得白天的训练如何
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.61,0:12:21.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都非常热情高涨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.44,0:12:24.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您这口气怎么像个上了年纪的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.70,0:12:26.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我本来就上了年纪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.32,0:12:30.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我之前拜托您的事情  想来听听结果
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.91,0:12:35.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先是淡岛  您觉得她怎样？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.75,0:12:37.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,持剑挥刀的姿势都非常不错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.38,0:12:40.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很适合作为其他队员的榜样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.67,0:12:43.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那说说她手下的几个小队长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.97,0:12:45.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比如说秋山
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.68,0:12:49.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的剑术也很强  平衡性仅次于淡岛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.64,0:12:51.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,镇守要地交给他就很让人放心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.10,0:12:52.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弁财
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.18,0:12:54.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中规中矩  却很靠得住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.56,0:12:57.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比较适合镇压对手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.77,0:12:58.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加茂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.65,0:13:00.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这位有些爱强出头
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.86,0:13:04.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,需要多加注意不要让他贸然行事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.32,0:13:06.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是这样的个性却能起到很大的作用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.61,0:13:07.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,道明寺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.66,0:13:12.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怪习惯不少  但是不要让他刻意去改正
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.91,0:13:13.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.25,0:13:16.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有其他表现出色的队员吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.46,0:13:19.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日高 五岛 布施 榎本
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.67,0:13:24.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你把这些怪人都集中在道明寺的小队  是有什么目的吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.92,0:13:27.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真要说  就当个玩具箱而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.26,0:13:29.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么问题吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.89,0:13:33.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有  如果他们能更正经点  还是不错的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.02,0:13:34.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看他们今后的表现吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.64,0:13:38.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊…  您觉得他怎样？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.10,0:13:39.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.52,0:13:43.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说楠原刚啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.11,0:13:45.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他挺有意思的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.36,0:13:47.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有意思啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.15,0:13:48.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很有意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.37,0:13:55.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他这么说哦  楠原
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.66,0:13:59.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.75,0:14:04.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这还真是难得一见  魔鬼居然会笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.13,0:14:07.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常感谢您的意见  我会作为参考的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.97,0:14:15.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秋山冰杜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.39,0:14:15.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.43,0:14:20.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从今日起隶属击剑机动科特务队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.81,0:14:22.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.23,0:14:23.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一个  弁财酉次郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.02,0:14:24.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.15,0:14:27.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你同样隶属击剑机动科特务
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.20,0:14:28.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.28,0:14:30.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一个  加茂刘芳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.95,0:14:31.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.66,0:14:32.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,道明寺安迪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.78,0:14:33.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.33,0:14:34.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日高晓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.58,0:14:35.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.79,0:14:36.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,楠原刚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.58,0:14:39.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,楠原刚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.54,0:14:41.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.75,0:14:46.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你将隶属庶务科资料室
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.21,0:14:47.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.93,0:14:51.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.93,0:14:55.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,庶务科资料室…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.72,0:14:58.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,庶务科资料室好像是善条先生那里吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.85,0:15:01.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等  等一下啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.90,0:15:05.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么只有他一个人被派去别的科室啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.78,0:15:09.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人员配置都是根据室长的计划安排的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.86,0:15:12.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们没有反驳的余地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.70,0:15:18.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日高是这么说的吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.79,0:15:20.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他还真是个热血青年呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.13,0:15:26.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么楠原  你有什么要问我的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.96,0:15:33.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是来质问我关于这次不合理的人事调动的理由吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.59,0:15:34.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  我没觉得这不合理…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.60,0:15:38.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟我总是给队里的前辈们添麻烦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.10,0:15:41.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但这并不是您的理由吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.85,0:15:48.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,室长您似乎非常看重善条先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.65,0:15:54.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我觉得您把我安排到这里  大概有什么特殊的用意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.32,0:15:55.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.70,0:16:00.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,善条先生  您在习惯新体制的scepter 4之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.12,0:16:03.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以暂时在资料室的工作以便“过渡”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.54,0:16:05.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们之前是这么约定的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.13,0:16:09.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但现在看来  您似乎已经喜欢上了那个昏暗的房间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.46,0:16:12.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  非常抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.18,0:16:17.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我也不能强行让鬼之善条服从命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.05,0:16:22.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若是拔去獠牙并加以驯养  那就不再是鬼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.64,0:16:24.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这还真是让人头疼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.11,0:16:29.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来我这圈子绕的有点大了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.86,0:16:32.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就直接了当说了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.57,0:16:37.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,善条先生希望您能够在我的Scepter 4中留下鬼的继承者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.87,0:16:38.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继承者？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.91,0:16:44.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说  如果您始终拒绝加入实战部队也无妨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.54,0:16:51.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相对的  我希望这位楠原队员能够继承您所有的技术
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.43,0:16:56.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,善条先生  下班了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.10,0:17:00.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天也辛苦你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.76,0:17:05.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天整理了资料架  还清理了水槽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.31,0:17:10.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还向事务室申请了新的电脑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.48,0:17:13.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.07,0:17:16.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那接下来我去准备晚饭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.70,0:17:17.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃荞麦面可以吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.53,0:17:22.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好啊  我们过来蹭饭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.45,0:17:25.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说你们今天也有紧急任务
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.42,0:17:29.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阝级的案件这周已经发生两件了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.50,0:17:31.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近这种事很多呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.09,0:17:36.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像这样经常紧急出动  还真是一点休息的时间都没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.01,0:17:39.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之我们这边的人手还不够
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.64,0:17:41.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你赶紧过来啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.35,0:17:45.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也很想啊  但…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.98,0:17:48.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不用这么谦逊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.81,0:17:52.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,楠原你不是已经拜了高手为师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.82,0:17:54.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来就会大幅升级了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.70,0:17:58.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟是特训班啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.45,0:18:03.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但具体要怎么做才能算“升级”呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.87,0:18:10.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宗像室长说  要我赢下淡岛副长一回合就算合格
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.01,0:18:25.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,副长  请多指教
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.35,0:18:27.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好  来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.78,0:18:36.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.91,0:18:40.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没完
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.30,0:18:59.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你完全不行啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.60,0:19:14.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,楠原  你那个动作是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.69,0:19:17.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个嘛  是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.65,0:19:19.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,楠原流剑法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.82,0:19:21.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,楠原流？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.57,0:19:23.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.37,0:19:26.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚开始我想请善条先生指导剑法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.08,0:19:30.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者让他传授我一些修行的方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.83,0:19:32.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可他说并没有这种东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.75,0:19:35.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  我是自成一派
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.96,0:19:40.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我就以平时和大家一起训练的剑道以及军刀术为基础
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.88,0:19:42.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再加上些善条先生独特风格加以改进
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.51,0:19:45.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,善条先生独特风格是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.39,0:19:46.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.47,0:19:51.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说到善条先生的动作  他拔刀时的气势相当骇人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.60,0:19:54.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但他平时却没那么剑拔弩张
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.44,0:19:57.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反而给人一种散漫的感觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.94,0:20:00.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像猎豹或者老虎的动作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.90,0:20:05.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,时刻准备着给猎物致命的一击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.70,0:20:07.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  所以我也试着模仿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.45,0:20:11.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,试试能不能学会他那种舒缓的动作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.46,0:20:12.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.87,0:20:15.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从舒缓的动作过度到瞬间爆发
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.25,0:20:20.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想用这个招式来赢过淡岛啊  楠原
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.30,0:20:22.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.01,0:20:25.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是这样打算的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.47,0:20:30.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  到此为止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.52,0:20:32.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抬走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.90,0:20:38.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里要接下攻击  然后这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.93,0:21:10.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也被打得太惨了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.61,0:21:23.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,楠原
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.82,0:21:25.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.99,0:21:30.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说你和淡岛君的比试好像进步挺大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.66,0:21:34.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但  气势还不够
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.96,0:21:38.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又或者说你太安于现状了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.58,0:21:39.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.50,0:21:42.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我差不多该给你定个期限了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.30,0:21:45.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就再给你一星期
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.51,0:21:47.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.63,0:21:50.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下周的共同训练是你最后的机会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.64,0:21:55.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在下一次的训练中  如果你的竹刀还碰不到淡岛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.19,0:22:01.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,楠原  我认为你不适合再当Scepter4的一员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.11,0:22:04.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你最好还是自己辞了这份工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.49,0:22:08.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一星期…辞职？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:09.11,0:22:09.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要被开除了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.95,0:22:13.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个  善条先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:13.83,0:22:15.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就像平时一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:16.12,0:22:16.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:21.29,0:22:22.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继续
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:23.63,0:22:24.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:29.09,0:22:30.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继续
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:31.80,0:22:32.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:36.73,0:22:37.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继续
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:38.44,0:22:38.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:53.28,0:22:55.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好啊  我们又来吃荞麦面了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:55.87,0:22:57.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,楠原呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:01.63,0:23:04.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这啊  真是个没用的家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:06.17,0:23:09.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有事的话我可以替你转达
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:09.09,0:23:11.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事  只是来看看他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:42.71,0:23:44.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天就是最后期限了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:49.88,0:23:50.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,室长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:50.97,0:23:52.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来完成度还挺高呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:53.30,0:23:55.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这下我非常期待明天的结果
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:56.01,0:23:56.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多谢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:57.22,0:23:57.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:58.97,0:24:00.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:00.23,0:24:03.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您干什么啊  善条先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:03.90,0:24:05.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天就到此为止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:10.07,0:24:12.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,副长  请多指教
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:12.40,0:24:13.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,楠原  加油啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:13.70,0:24:14.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:14.66,0:24:16.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你今天可要多撑一会啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:18.12,0:24:19.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不觉得他有点走路一瘸一拐的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:21.96,0:24:22.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:29.71,0:24:31.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又被那个假动作给骗了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:44.31,0:24:47.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好棒啊  打中她的巨乳了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:49.44,0:24:50.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:53.61,0:24:55.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站起来  楠原
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:55.53,0:24:56.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:02.00,0:25:05.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才那击虽然不算重  但你确实打中了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:07.13,0:25:09.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你合格了  楠原刚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:15.26,0:25:19.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以新的人事调动稍后会来通知我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:19.76,0:25:20.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:21.72,0:25:23.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…善条先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:24.18,0:25:27.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢您一直以来的指导
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:27.98,0:25:30.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别这么说  我根本没教什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:30.65,0:25:31.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  我真的很感谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:32.74,0:25:34.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,善条先生您光是站在我面前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:35.40,0:25:39.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我光看着您的背影就感觉学到了不少
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:40.66,0:25:45.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像眼前有一座高山  就忍不住想去爬…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:46.54,0:25:48.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个比喻好像有点不太对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:49.71,0:25:52.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有你陪我  我也过得很开心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:54.47,0:25:55.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常感谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:55.55,0:25:58.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果能令您过得开心  那是我的荣幸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:59.93,0:26:01.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打扰了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:02.31,0:26:02.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:03.02,0:26:04.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用管我  你们自便
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:07.23,0:26:09.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,楠原  白天的事恭喜你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:11.27,0:26:14.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到你还真能从那个淡岛的手中拿下一回合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:16.40,0:26:18.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,善条先生也让人大开眼界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:18.95,0:26:22.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨晚你打在楠原脚上的那一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:25.91,0:26:29.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在意识到自己跨出去的脚上使不上力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:29.88,0:26:34.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的身体会在无意识中做出另一项最好的选择
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:35.26,0:26:39.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,善条先生  你故意打伤他的一只脚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:39.80,0:26:42.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是为了引出他的这份力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:42.72,0:26:44.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真美的指导
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:44.64,0:26:46.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是楠原他自身的才能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:47.18,0:26:50.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就收下这份才能了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:51.11,0:26:54.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,楠原  我命令你调去特务队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:54.94,0:26:59.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今后还请活用你的才能来守住我的背后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:00.99,0:27:01.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:01.87,0:27:05.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么就从现在开始  也能帮我擦一下背吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:08.21,0:27:08.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:10.46,0:27:16.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然  我也没有放弃那位身经百战的老手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:17.30,0:27:19.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样啊  善条先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:20.01,0:27:26.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您有没有兴趣再次站上前线  近距离见证楠原的成长啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:26.93,0:27:28.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么说呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:29.69,0:27:33.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还挺喜欢那个昏暗的房间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:34.15,0:27:39.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那里我能清楚地看见队员们训练时的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:43.57,0:27:47.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那景象太过耀眼不是我这种人能介入的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:01.55,0:28:05.27,Default,,0,0,999,,找楠原商量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:09.93,0:28:10.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,善条先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:13.02,0:28:14.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,楠原他…
